# SPRINT 4: Frontend Alignment — HIAS Core

You are working on a Go insurance backend (DDD + Clean Architecture). This sprint adds endpoints the frontend dashboard needs that don't exist yet. The backend has 200+ endpoints working — these are the specific gaps the frontend agent expects. Each task creates a new handler method, route, and (where needed) a new service method or SQL query.

**Rules:**
- Follow existing code conventions (see CLAUDE.md)
- Money is BIGINT (cents), int64 in Go
